<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="6Sep1920"><font color="red">6 September 1920</font>, <cite>Letters I</cite> (JJ to Carlo Linati): I am working like a galleyslave, an ass, a brute. I cannot even sleep. The episode of <cite>Circe</cite> has changed me too into an animal.</div>
